LATEST - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-man-ipsla-oper:ipsla/operation-data/operations/operation/{operation-id}/statistics/latest/

Retrieve operation of resource: latest

operation-id: string
in path

ID of operation-id

200 OK
latest_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

HOUR - Retrieve

operation-id: string
in path

ID of operation-id

hour-index: string
in path

ID of hour-index

200 OK
hour_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request
